1.10	We_Are_Together_(film)	We Are Together	We Are Together (Thina Simunye) is a British documentary film about the orphanage "Agape" in South Africa. Children, who live here, lost their parents to AIDS. The film is full of songs, both native and English. Eventually the children get a chance to visit New York and raise money by singing for the public.	http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/7/7d/We_Are_Together_%28film%29.jpg
